# Modify player character races to have a traits pool, but equipped with the "No Traits" pseudo-trait as a default.
# In this way, PCs can easily be modified, and NPCs will not be flagged as needing their traits selected.

###Block: Standard races
# Race Name		Apply Kit
Dwarf.MOD		KIT:1|Character Traits
Elf.MOD		KIT:1|Character Traits
Gnome.MOD		KIT:1|Character Traits
Half-Elf.MOD	KIT:1|Character Traits
Half-Orc.MOD	KIT:1|Character Traits
Halfling.MOD	KIT:1|Character Traits
Human.MOD		KIT:1|Character Traits

